
docker save <image_name> > <image_name>.tar
docker load < <image_name>.tar

docker tag <image_name> <new_image_name>


docker run --mount type=bind;source=/data/neo4j;target=/data/neo4j (this is the new way of mouting filesystem on Docker)

Storage driver:
  AUFS, Overlay, Overlay2, DeviceMapper, ZFS ...
  It depends on the Host OS which storage driver will be used by Docker
  
  
